		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Rod - Very Rare (Requires Attunement)</em></p><p>This rod has the following properties.</p><p><strong>Alertness.</strong> While holding the rod, you have Advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks and on Initiative rolls.</p><p><strong>Spells.</strong> While holding the rod, you can cast the following spells from it:</p><ul><li><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.KzJ4ChPXHr2MnGbz]{Detect Evil and Good}</em></p></li><li><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.zWjDq2YlL1XWOcji]{Detect Magic}</em></p></li><li><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.1gqMmxF2RFCK9khd]{Detect Poison and Disease}</em></p></li><li><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.Wp9ckwdiUpIuPE5l]{See Invisibility}</em></p></li></ul><p><strong>Protective Aura.</strong> As a Action, you can plant the haft end of the rod in the ground, whereupon the rod's head sheds Bright Light in a 60-foot radius and Dim Light for an additional 60 feet. While in that Bright Light, you and your allies gain a +1 bonus to &amp;reference[Armor Class] and saving throws and can sense the location of any Invisible creature that is also in the Bright Light.</p><p>The rod's head stops glowing and the effect ends after 10 minutes or when a creature takes a Action to pull the rod from the ground. Once used, this property can't be used again until the next dawn.</p><section><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The <strong>Plant Rod</strong> activity can be used to place a 60 foot template representing the Bright Light radius. It includes an Active Effect which can be applied to the relevant Actors and adds the +1 bonus to AC and Saving Throws.</p></section>",
